framework/claude/skills/sdd-roadmap/SKILL.md:21-28|framework/claude/skills/sdd-roadmap/refs/review.md:5-14|NG: router accepts feature-less `--cross-check` / `--wave`, but review ref still requires `{feature}` and misclassifies the flags as review type
framework/claude/skills/sdd-roadmap/refs/review.md:75-79,133-138|framework/claude/skills/sdd-roadmap/refs/revise.md:251-259|NG: cross-cutting verdict destination exists, but review execution flow has no matching cross-cutting scope route
